{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"continueTransaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The messages within a transaction carry the cumulative values of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a field. In case one or more messages within a transaction are not","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"received by the Server (e.g., as a result of radio collisions),","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the next received message will make up for the lost messages,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"carrying cumulative values of the field."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A new transaction is started when this field is set to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or when the last message of the transaction was sent 6 or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"more seconds earlier."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This defaults to "},{"code":"false","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", which means that each new message will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"receive a new transaction identifier (if not set explicitly)."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/SceneRecall\/continueTransaction"},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/scenerecall\/continuetransaction"],"traits":