essage should start a new transaction.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/SceneRecall\/continueTransaction","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/scenerecall\/continuetransaction","role":"symbol"}}}